  "text": "In addition, HsCRP is reported to be associated with cancer prognosis, and a recent study validated the ability of preoperative hsCRP to predict postoperative prognosis among cancer patients. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] However, data are inadequate regarding whether pre-or postoperative hsCRP levels have better predictive value after oncologic surgery.",
